@shahsank3t Thanks for working on it. I've tested this PR locally and found out the following thing:
* the UI cannot route to the correct page after clicking "save" button for "Add Table" for the first time. There is a circle that keeps spinning. 
* when clicking into "Add Table", after typing the table name, the UI will prompt "schema not found" on the top right side of the UI.

@jackjlli @npawar 
Thanks for taking the time to try out the changes.
I have updated the PR with the reported issues and concerns.

> @galalen is there anything pending in this PR?

@kishoreg, @npawar Yes, I'm working on unit and the integration test.
I want to make sure reading the IdealState will give me the current state.
